{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"htmlAst":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"There are several layers of configuration for the site and you can go as deep as\nyou want or need."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h1","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"site-config.xml"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Much of the configuration for the site can be defined in "},{"type":"element","tagName":"code","properties":{"className":["language-text"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"site-config.xml"}]},{"type":"text","value":". This\nis not a standard Gatsby configuration file and is specific to this starter. The\ncontents of the file are well commented. By changing the content of this file\nyou can customise many aspects of the site. The data defined in this file is\nused to:"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"ul","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"construct pages"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"display data"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"supply data to plugins"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"configure and enable / disable features"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h1","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Plugins"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Gatsby uses a plugin architecture to add additional functionality. This starter\nuses a large number of plugins which are configured via "},{"type":"element","tagName":"code","properties":{"className":["language-text"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"gatsby-config.js"}]},{"type":"text","value":". All\nplugin configuration is found there, or in individual files for each plugin\nwithin the "},{"type":"element","tagName":"code","properties":{"className":["language-text"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"/config"}]},{"type":"text","value":" directory. Many of the plugins draw configuration options\nfrom "},{"type":"element","tagName":"code","properties":{"className":["language-text"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"site-config.xml"}]},{"type":"text","value":", however you can also edit the plugin configuration\ndirectly to further customise the behaviour and features offered by the plugins."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h1","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Styling"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"This site uses "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://github.com/Undistraction/cssapi"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"CSSAPI"}]},{"type":"text","value":" to define\nstyles used throughout the site. This gives you a single, centralised location\nto make changes to color, fonts and spacing amongst other things. Style\nconfiguration can be found in "},{"type":"element","tagName":"code","properties":{"className":["language-text"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"src/components/styles/api.js"}]},{"type":"text","value":"."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h1","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Components"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"The site uses\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://github.com/styled-components/styled-components"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Styled Components"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\nthroughout. Pages and the components within them are each defined as a separate\ncomponent found in "},{"type":"element","tagName":"code","properties":{"className":["language-text"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"src/components"}]},{"type":"text","value":". Components used in more than one location\ncan be found in "},{"type":"element","tagName":"code","properties":{"className":["language-text"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"src/components/shared"}]},{"type":"text","value":". Note that elements generated from\nmarkdown are also transformed into components. This mapping of generic HTML\nelements to components happens in "},{"type":"element","tagName":"code","properties":{"className":["language-text"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"src/components/shared/MarkdownContent.jsx"}]},{"type":"text","value":"."}]}],"data":{"quirksMode":false}},"wordCount":{"words":247},"timeToRead":1,"frontmatter":{"keywords":"settings, config","image":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1.7772020725388602,"src":"/gatsby-starter-skeleton/static/main-e4ca53d1d9f3aed86588abbaa1fd48b8-381d6.jpg","srcSet":"/gatsby-starter-skeleton/static/main-e4ca53d1d9f3aed86588abbaa1fd48b8-62f05.jpg 200w,\n/gatsby-starter-skeleton/static/main-e4ca53d1d9f3aed86588abbaa1fd48b8-dc2b4.jpg 400w,\n/gatsby-starter-skeleton/static/main-e4ca53d1d9f3aed86588abbaa1fd48b8-381d6.jpg 800w,\n/gatsby-starter-skeleton/static/main-e4ca53d1d9f3aed86588abbaa1fd48b8-e5d70.jpg 1200w,\n/gatsby-starter-skeleton/static/main-e4ca53d1d9f3aed86588abbaa1fd48b8-d14e0.jpg 1600w,\n/gatsby-starter-skeleton/static/main-e4ca53d1d9f3aed86588abbaa1fd48b8-9e67f.jpg 2400w,\n/gatsby-starter-skeleton/static/main-e4ca53d1d9f3aed86588abbaa1fd48b8-e9bbf.jpg 2401w","sizes":"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px"}}}},"fields":{"title":"Configuration","tags":["settings","config"],"date":"30th May 2018","category":"Configuration